    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes how an Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP)
   session is mapped onto a QUIC connection.  EPP over QUIC (EoQ)
   leverages the performance and security features of the QUIC protocol
   as an EPP transport.

	 </t>
